<ul>
<li><span class="citation journal">David Wagle (April 1998). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://linuxgazette.net./issue27/wagle.html">"Evangelism: A Unix Bigot and Linux Advocate's Spewings"</a>. <i>Linux Gazette</i> <b>27</b>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOperating+system+advocacy&amp;rft.atitle=Evangelism%3A+A+Unix+Bigot+and+Linux+Advocate%27s+Spewings&amp;rft.au=David+Wagle&amp;rft.aulast=David+Wagle&amp;rft.date=April+1998&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Flinuxgazette.net.%2Fissue27%2Fwagle.html&amp;rft.jtitle=Linux+Gazette&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.volume=27" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><span class="citation journal">Nikolai Bezroukov (1998-06-01). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.softpanorama.org/OSS/bad_linux_advocacy_faq.shtml"><i>Bad Linux Advocacy FAQ</i></a>. 0.81.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOperating+system+advocacy&amp;rft.aulast=Nikolai+Bezroukov&amp;rft.au=Nikolai+Bezroukov&amp;rft.btitle=Bad+Linux+Advocacy+FAQ&amp;rft.date=1998-06-01&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.softpanorama.org%2FOSS%2Fbad_linux_advocacy_faq.shtml&amp;rft.series=0.81&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.writingonyourpalm.net/column040315.htm">Writing On Your Palm: Ford vs Chevy</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://wired-vig.wired.com/news/print/0,1294,57280,00.html">Mac, Windows War Ends in Truce</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.macvswindows.com/">Mac vs. Windows</a> (Dead link)</li>
